high_descs: Turn right then walk straight then turn left straight to the cabinet above the stove
Get the bowl in the cabinet right above the stove
Turn to your left then walk straight turn left face the fridge
Open the fridge put in the bowl wait a seconds then pick it up and close the fridge
Turn to your right and head to the cabinet beside the fridge
Put in the bowl inside the cabinet beside the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put in the chilled bowl inside the cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the oven and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the rightmost small upper cabinet door and take out the black bowl out of the cabinet, then close the door.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the bowl inside then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the bowl, then close the fridge door.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and take a step forward, turn left to face the fridge.
Open the cabinet below the counter in front of you and put the chilled bowl inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in a cabinet.

high_descs: Walk to the stove and look up at the cupboards above the stove.
Open the cupboard on the right and take out a black bowl.
Move to the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge door, place the bowl inside, close the door, open the door and take the bowl out, close the door.
Move to the counter to the right of the fridge and look at the cupboard below the counter.
Open the cupboard door, place the bowl inside, and close the cupboard door.
anns.task_desc: To chill a bowl and place it in the cupboard.
